namespace Pizza

features
	Pizza {abstract}	
		mandatory
			Topping	
				or
					Salami
					Ham
					Mozzarella
			Size	
				alternative
					Normal
					Big
			Dough	
				alternative
					Neapolitan
					Sicilian

		optional
			CheesyCrust

		mandatory
			OR {abstract}	
				or
					CheesyCrust_1 {abstract}
					Sicilian_1 {abstract}
					Big_1 {abstract}

constraints
	!Neapolitan | !Salami
	!Neapolitan | !Ham
	CheesyCrust_1 => !CheesyCrust
	Sicilian_1 => !Sicilian
	Big_1 => Big